# The platform stack — four layers

- Cloud object storage — S3 / ADLS / GCS: the durable base for your bytes
- Delta Lake — open table format: ACID transactions, schema, time travel over those files
- Unity Catalog — governance: names, secures & audits every asset through one namespace
- Engines on top — Spark/Photon, Databricks SQL, Lakeflow — all sharing one copy
- Delta Lake + Unity Catalog get the deep dive in module 02
